{"tid":2404934,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"巴爾發文公開打臉摩帥？ 他這一句話惹摩帥惱火","createTime":"2021-02-12T04:42:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-12T08:32:46.000Z","uid":147522,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"346e864700c62ee5e885642e14a6457d58b42082","tid":2404934,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T04:42:40.000Z","msg":"　　據英國媒體稱，巴爾和摩連奴之間發生了問題。<br />\n<br />\n　　巴爾沒有參與對愛華頓的足總盃賽，摩連奴稱威爾斯人訓練中感覺不好，但在 Instagram平台上，巴爾卻發文稱：「今天練的很好」，這和摩帥的說法完全相反。<br />\n<br />\n　　《鏡報》稱，摩帥對巴爾的這種表態感到不快，認為威爾斯人這是公開和自己唱反調。在對愛華頓賽後，摩帥曾說：「巴爾沒進名單，是因為他對自己訓練中的表現不滿意。」"},{"pid":"7009c75f0fe833b953001d014e2b26fd19bd354e","tid":2404934,"uid":47303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T06:27:07.000Z","msg":"屌你老母快手退休啦"},{"pid":"16c9daa7323fe1638b3d2a983dfdb968f781d52d","tid":2404934,"uid":137605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7009c75f0fe833b953001d014e2b26fd19bd354e","tid":2404934,"uid":47303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T06:27:07.000Z","msg":"屌你老母快手退休啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T06:28:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f1491902a346739bf6e9cc3964641063d49266c","tid":2404934,"uid":47303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16c9daa7323fe1638b3d2a983dfdb968f781d52d","tid":2404934,"uid":137605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7009c75f0fe833b953001d014e2b26fd19bd354e","tid":2404934,"uid":47303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T06:27:07.000Z","msg":"屌你老母快手退休啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T06:28:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T06:28:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"673efbe8249bf07a2ec9d0b5ab97b01fb866bdae","tid":2404934,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T06:34:03.000Z",